        <updateDate>2019-01-07T17:41:26Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>STEM Opportunities Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill provides for guidance, data collection, and grants related to women and minorities in science, technology, engineering, and mathematics at institutions of higher education and at federal science agencies.</p> <p>]]></text>
      </summary>
